Numeric Comparison

Compare pond stats

We know the watersheds have different numbering, so first need to renumber all to match

pond <- shedno_update2(pond) %>% arrange(ShedNo)
orig_pond <- shedno_update2(orig_pond) %>% arrange(ShedNo)

Original Pond data

New Pond data

Differences

c <- compare(pond, orig_pond)
## Pit Rec not all the same, but all within 1 cell
## Not all PreVol the same
## Pit Vol not the same, but within 1
## Varatio not the same, but within 5
## Pit area not the same, but within 3 cells
## Not all NextPit the same
## In Rec not all the same, but all within 1 cell
## Out Rec not all the same, but all within 1 cell
## Out elev not all the same, but within 0.01
## Not all Stage the same
## Not all Visited the same
  • All important values (pit area, pit vol, varatio, becomes) are identical, or only different by a small degree
  • Nextpit is often incorrect (not sure why)
  • PreVol is not used by LITAP (FlowMapR required it to properly calculate PitVol)
  • Stage and visited are not used by LITAP
  • Exact location of pourpoint between two watersheds is sometimes off by a cell or two (out seqno and in seqno)
  • Exact location of center pit cell is sometimes off by a cell or two, for example:
